{"tid":1877150,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"利物浦最大爭標對手","createTime":"2020-02-13T00:21:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-16T17:09:46.000Z","uid":186,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"03e9286faafbd9de568792a0de8b779e196cb873","tid":1877150,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T00:21:34.000Z","msg":"利物浦目前在英超聯賽遙遙領先排第二位的曼城22分，餘下13輪賽事只要多拿18分即可提早首度在英超封王。連最大對手曼城早前也宣布「投降」，似乎已沒有任何東西可以阻礙他們。<br />\n<br />\n可是新型冠狀病毒近日入侵英國，武漢肺炎確診者人數急增至8人，更出現一名來自白禮頓的「超級帶菌者」，一人將病毒傳給9人。疫情未在英國社區爆發，但部分敏感的利物浦球迷已經開始擔心起來。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有利迷在Twitter表示：「我很擔心。新型冠狀病毒會阻止利物浦贏得英超冠軍嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n另一人亦稱：「假如冠狀病毒最終令利物浦失去聯賽冠軍，我想不應該受不了那些嘲笑memes。」<br />\n<br />\n也有球迷說，「利物浦最大爭標對手竟然是冠狀病毒，這令我很憤怒。」"},{"pid":"a4ad0c6c3e3574d81c8e68d62311a88720384bbd","tid":1877150,"uid":186,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T00:28:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oNUcViV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoNUcViV.png&h=0f6cfc96&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2V1yELA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2V1yELA.png&h=64153cea&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oRvfS5B.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoRvfS5B.png&h=b597000a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ezw3hxg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEzw3hxg.png&h=dfadf675&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RWqWCxh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRWqWCxh.png&h=492de183&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vrixaSi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvrixaSi.png&h=ab62c1b8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"66356f2790070ca69f3bf318095b4b3fd81db232","tid":1877150,"uid":186,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T00:28:40.000Z","msg":"武漢返英國民在利物浦市醫院隔離<br />\n<br />\n曼聯在冬季轉會窗離奇由上海申花借入前鋒恩哈路，日前已有球迷開玩笑說，這是曼聯阻止死敵利物浦首奪英超的終極武器：借恩哈路令英國引入武漢肺炎病毒，然後聯賽被迫取消，利物浦遂無法贏得英超。不過也有樂觀球迷認為，即使是武漢肺炎也阻止不了紅軍奪冠。<br />\n<br />\n利迷的憂慮，其實不是完全毫無道理，事關83名自武漢返回英國的國民，已入住利物浦身處的默西塞特郡一所醫院隔離14天，在醫院附近居住的居民已表達憂慮，但當局認為公眾毋須擔心。另有消息指，利物浦市已出現首宗武漢肺炎確診個案，但目前官方渠道暫時未能證實。不過那位來自白禮頓的「超級帶菌者」經已完全康復出院，可稍為降低社區爆發的憂慮。"},{"pid":"ffccc146eed713f944f52c3024cfdd4102330277","tid":1877150,"uid":186,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T00:30:19.000Z","msg":"而家身處英國疫區Brighton，求安慰<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1877090\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1877090</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n隔離巴打都開post了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2aa50bd626e77eee8c39da2c0b94fce314f29f14","tid":1877150,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T04:35:12.000Z","msg":"橙"},{"pid":"6649948b4dce36637848b61a32e0efe6660818cf","tid":1877150,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T05:13:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f558c62ce6573304cd3e2373a56d81d7c525135","tid":1877150,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6649948b4dce36637848b61a32e0efe6660818cf","tid":1877150,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T05:13:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T10:06:33.000Z","msg":"無人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bb7a9c9c3c80f6a8675270fdc0b597929bc8f34","tid":1877150,"uid":2884